00:19:49,320 --> 00:19:51,080
你可以悄悄溜走
and you can slip away.

367
00:19:52,190 --> 00:19:54,710
你的情人会用她自己的信用卡订房
Your lover pays with a credit card in her own name.

368
00:19:54,840 --> 00:19:59,880
你应该会用现金还她 但这不重要
I assume you split it in cash, but that’s immaterial.

369
00:20:00,020 --> 00:20:01,710
她叫什么也不重要
As is her name.

370
00:20:03,130 --> 00:20:06,550
重要的是你最喜欢那套可以俯瞰整座城市的初级套房
The junior suite with city view is your favorite.

371
00:20:09,580 --> 00:20:11,170
我说了我不喜欢说谎的人
I don’t like liars.

372
00:20:13,760 --> 00:20:15,830
我的天 别动 不要动
Fucking hell! Wait, don’t move it.

373
00:20:15,970 --> 00:20:17,250
不要动 别踏马动了
Don’t move it. Don’t fucking move it!

374
00:20:17,380 --> 00:20:18,940
我来处理
Okay, I got it. I got it. I got it.

375
00:20:19,070 --> 00:20:22,460
这是你最无聊的招
That is the most boring thing you’ve ever done.

376
00:20:23,870 --> 00:20:25,050
-把手放下 -不要移动
-Hands down. -Stay still. Stay still.

377
00:20:25,180 --> 00:20:26,770
看着我 看着我
Look at me. Look at me.

378
00:20:26,910 --> 00:20:27,980
好样的 你给我等着瞧
All right, I’ll swap you.

379
00:20:28,120 --> 00:20:28,390
-好 -把手臂给我
- Okay. - Give me the arm.

380
00:20:32,260 --> 00:20:35,990
我在想你是不是用药过猛了
I wonder if it’s possible you went just a bit heavy

381
00:20:36,130 --> 00:20:37,990
你的吐真剂
on the DZM 5.

382
00:20:38,130 --> 00:20:40,100
也许吧
I may well have.

383
00:20:42,550 --> 00:20:44,790
刚刚你看出什么来了吗
Did you see what you needed to see?

384
00:20:44,930 --> 00:20:46,240
还没有
I don’t know yet.

385
00:20:46,380 --> 00:20:49,830
今晚只是个引子 马上好戏开场
That was the rock. Now I watch the ripples.

386
00:20:54,320 --> 00:20:55,590
先别收拾了
Leave the rest.

387
00:20:55,730 --> 00:20:57,290
马上
I will.

388
00:20:57,420 --> 00:20:59,390
两分钟就好
Just give me two minutes.

389
00:21:02,190 --> 00:21:04,020
别管了
Leave it.

390
00:21:04,150 --> 00:21:06,020
马上就来
I will.

391
00:21:07,260 --> 00:21:08,710
它是干什么的
What does it do?

392
00:21:08,850 --> 00:21:10,750
什么是干什么的
What does what do?

393
00:21:10,890 --> 00:21:12,920
死危病毒(赛维鲁斯)
Severus.

394
00:21:13,060 --> 00:21:15,720
这恐怕不能告诉你
I’m afraid that’s in the black bag.

395
00:21:18,690 --> 00:21:19,760
那我来猜一猜
Want me to guess?

396
00:21:19,890 --> 00:21:21,790
别
No.

397
00:21:21,930 --> 00:21:26,280
是下三滥的手段吗 比如说能让整个政府瘫痪的恶意软件
Dirty tricks, malware, meant to disable a government.

398
00:21:28,800 --> 00:21:30,010
为什么这么说
Why would you say that?

399
00:21:30,150 --> 00:21:33,150
就像赛维鲁斯·亚历山大
Hmm? Oh, Severus Alexander.

400
00:21:33,290 --> 00:21:35,700
那位罗马皇帝
You know, the Roman emperor whose, uh...

401
00:21:35,840 --> 00:21:40,220
因为他被刺杀导致了长达50年的内战
uh, assassination led to 50 years of civil war.

402
00:21:42,090 --> 00:21:43,120
你要这么想的话
If you like.

403
00:21:43,260 --> 00:21:46,330
我想的是你 快点来吧
You know what I like. Hurry up.

404
00:21:49,340 --> 00:21:50,720
乔治
George.

405
00:21:50,860 --> 00:21:52,380
来了
Sorry.

406
00:21:53,930 --> 00:21:55,860
来这儿
Come here.

407
00:22:02,760 --> 00:22:06,250
如果你遇到了问题需要我的帮助
If you were in a situation, if you needed my help...

408
00:22:06,390 --> 00:22:08,460
我现在的确需要你的帮助
I do need your help.

409
00:22:09,840 --> 00:22:11,700
给我挠挠背
Scratch my back.

410
00:22:14,330 --> 00:22:17,120
-不管是什么困难 -别说了
-Wouldn’t matter what it was... -Please stop talking.

411
00:22:18,610 --> 00:22:20,330
我都会来帮你
I would do anything for you.

412
00:22:20,470 --> 00:22:22,090
真的吗
Would you?

413
00:22:22,230 --> 00:22:23,370
真的
Yes.

414
00:22:23,510 --> 00:22:25,270
不管任何事情吗
Anything at all?

415
00:22:25,410 --> 00:22:27,000
对
Yes.

416
00:22:28,790 --> 00:22:30,650
你会撒谎吗
Would you lie?

417
00:22:32,350 --> 00:22:35,560
我不会对你撒谎
Yes. But never to you.

418
00:22:35,690 --> 00:22:37,870
你真好
That’s sweet.

419
00:22:38,010 --> 00:22:40,250
你会欺骗我吗
Would you lie to me?

420
00:22:40,390 --> 00:22:42,560
我不会 除非万不得已的时候
Only if I had to.

421
00:22:45,460 --> 00:22:48,360
-乔治 哪怕是为我杀人你也愿意吗 -愿意
-Would you kill for me, George? -Yes.

422
00:22:48,500 --> 00:22:49,920
-真的吗 -万死不辞
-Would you? -Yes.

423
00:23:03,580 --> 00:23:05,340
我要去睡了
I’m going to bed.

424
00:23:08,210 --> 00:23:10,250
你怎么了
What’s wrong?

425
00:23:10,380 --> 00:23:11,940
没怎么
Nothing.

426
00:23:17,700 --> 00:23:19,530
这周末怎么样
Maybe this weekend?

427
00:23:24,260 --> 00:23:26,160
找个好看点的地方
Someplace nice.

428
00:23:28,820 --> 00:23:31,030
别熬太晚
Don’t stay up too late.

429
00:23:55,980 --> 00:23:57,570
不会吧
The fuck?

430
00:24:24,630 --> 00:24:26,390
等下
Wait, wait, wait.

431
00:24:26,530 --> 00:24:29,460
菲尔怎么了
Phil? Phil?

432
00:24:49,030 --> 00:24:51,040
这周要不要去看个电影
I thought maybe a movie this week.

433
00:24:51,170 --> 00:24:55,110
我礼拜三要出国了 礼拜四回来
Uh, I’m out of the country Wednesday, back Thursday.

434
00:24:55,250 --> 00:24:56,590
那就明天吧
Maybe tomorrow, then.

435
00:24:56,730 --> 00:24:58,660
好
Sure.

436
00:25:00,490 --> 00:25:02,290
最近有什么新上映的电影吗
Is anything playing?

437
00:25:02,430 --> 00:25:04,390
我听说《暗窗》不错
I hear Dark Windowsis good.

438
00:25:04,530 --> 00:25:06,530
《暗窗》
Dark Windows.

439
00:25:06,670 --> 00:25:08,640
没听说过
Don’t know that one.

440
00:25:10,260 --> 00:25:12,200
那要不要去看
Should we see it?

441
00:25:12,330 --> 00:25:13,580
好啊
Love to.

442
00:25:27,660 --> 00:25:30,110
你周三要去哪里
Where are you off to on Wednesday?

443
00:25:34,040 --> 00:25:35,840
黑袋行动
Black bag.

444
00:25:35,980 --> 00:25:36,980
好
Right.

445
00:26:03,630 --> 00:26:04,900
乔治·伍德豪斯
George Woodhouse.

446
00:26:05,040 --> 00:26:08,180
我忘了带工牌了 能给我个临时工牌吗
Forgot my badge. Can I get a temporary?

447
00:26:12,570 --> 00:26:14,290
工牌制度非常重要 伍德豪斯先生
Proper badge protocol is essential, Mr. Woodhouse.

448
00:26:14,430 --> 00:26:16,020
我下次一定不会忘
Never happen again.

449
00:26:34,070 --> 00:26:36,280
-派对很不错 -很高兴你能来参加
-Great party. -Glad you could make it.

450
00:26:36,420 --> 00:26:37,900
我的手指还能动
Fingers still work.

451
00:26:38,040 --> 00:26:39,730
我知道她是个疯婆子
Look, I know she’s crazy as a fucking loon,

452
00:26:39,870 --> 00:26:41,460
但她让我感到快乐
but she makes me happy.

453
00:26:41,600 --> 00:26:43,420
我全部的人生 都奉献给了人民
My whole life, all I’ve done is do for people,

454
00:26:43,560 --> 00:26:44,600
苏珊和我的孩子们
Susan and the kids.

455
00:26:44,740 --> 00:26:46,320
结果大家都恨我
I get nothing but hate for it.

456
00:26:46,460 --> 00:26:48,910
克拉丽莎对此毫无期待
Clarissa expects exactly nothing.

457
00:26:49,050 --> 00:26:50,120
好吧
Okay.

458
00:26:50,260 --> 00:26:52,780
你听说米查姆的事了吗
You’ve heard about Meacham?

459
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:54,610
他死了 冠状动脉出了问题
He’s dead. Coronary.

460
00:26:54,750 --> 00:26:56,090
-什么时候的事 -昨晚
-When? -Last night.

461
00:26:56,230 --> 00:26:58,820
-我才见过他 -人们总这么说
-I just saw him. -People always say that.

462
00:26:58,960 --> 00:27:01,650
这么年轻就犯心脏病了 你觉得呢
Little young for a heart attack, don’t you think?

463
00:27:01,790 --> 00:27:03,060
是的
Yes.

464
00:27:03,200 --> 00:27:05,830
你知道他在忙什么任务吗
Do you know what he was working on?

465
00:27:05,960 --> 00:27:07,280
不知道
No.

466
00:27:07,410 --> 00:27:09,110
我得去见凯瑟琳
I need to see Kathryn.

467
00:27:09,240 --> 00:27:12,140
施蒂格利茨和她在一起 你可能要
She’s got Stieglitz in there. You might want to...

468
00:27:35,300 --> 00:27:37,270
都到齐了 手上的任务
...all here, the task at hand,

469
00:27:37,410 --> 00:27:40,340
是诉说过去一个半月对你
to fully express those needs and desire to you

470
00:27:40,480 --> 00:27:42,030
的那些需求和渴望
over the last month and a half.

471
00:27:42,170 --> 00:27:44,760
但我见过吗 我是否
But have I seen it? Do I...

472
00:27:52,010 --> 00:27:54,010
抱歉打扰了
Sorry to interrupt.

473
00:27:55,840 --> 00:27:58,500
你的钥匙为什么在我的包里
Why would your key be in my bag?

474
00:27:58,640 --> 00:28:01,470
我在衣柜底部发现了它 我猜是你的
Found it on the closet floor and thought it was yours.

475
00:28:01,610 --> 00:28:03,680
它们长得都一样
They all look alike.

476
00:28:05,710 --> 00:28:07,850
我的包在桌子上
My bag’s by the desk.

477
00:28:07,990 --> 00:28:10,200
下午一点前 钥匙还给我
I need my key back by 1:00.

478
00:28:10,340 --> 00:28:12,200
两分钟
Two minutes.

479
00:28:13,130 --> 00:28:14,550
你没事吧
You okay?

480
00:28:14,690 --> 00:28:17,480
我听说了米查姆的事
I just heard about Meacham.

481
00:28:17,620 --> 00:28:19,280
太可怕了
Terrible.

482
00:28:21,350 --> 00:28:22,390
还有其他消息吗
Anything else?

483
00:28:22,520 --> 00:28:24,280
没了
No.

484
00:28:24,420 --> 00:28:26,730
如果你不介意 回家的路上给自己买点吃的
Grab yourself something on the way home, if you don’t mind.

485
00:28:26,870 --> 00:28:29,190
我可能要去湖边
I might stop off at the lake.

486
00:29:27,830 --> 00:29:29,450
苏黎世湖
Zurich?

487
00:29:33,940 --> 00:29:37,630
47.3701 北
47.3701 north,

488
00:29:37,770 --> 00:29:40,950
8.5411 东
8.5411 east.

489
00:29:51,060 --> 00:29:53,790
不好意思 我迟到了
Sorry. Running behind.

490
00:29:53,930 --> 00:29:55,340
没事
Mm-hmm.

491
00:29:58,170 --> 00:30:00,310
我们能晚几分钟开始吗
Can you go a few minutes late?

492
00:30:01,970 --> 00:30:05,180
访谈不超过45分钟 我就无法解除命令
If we don’t do 45, I can’t clear the mandate.

493
00:30:05,320 --> 00:30:09,110
那就2点6分开始
Uh, I make that 2:06.

494
00:30:10,360 --> 00:30:12,050
好吧
Fine.

495
00:30:28,890 --> 00:30:30,960
我仍然时睡时醒
Uh, sleep remains inconsistent.

496
00:30:31,100 --> 00:30:36,970
我服用了2.5至3毫克劳拉西泮
I take two-point-five to three milligrams of lorazepam,

497
00:30:37,110 --> 00:30:39,900
晚上8点服用了一次 11点又服用了一次
the first at 8:00, the second at 11:00

498
00:30:40,040 --> 00:30:42,180
夜间做噩梦后
and the third in the night.

499
00:30:43,180 --> 00:30:44,700
又服用了一次
After the first nightmare.

500
00:30:44,840 --> 00:30:47,460
还是每晚做噩梦吗
You’re still having them every night?

501
00:30:48,840 --> 00:30:50,400
是的
Yes.

502
00:30:50,530 --> 00:30:53,230
草药能帮助我入睡
Um... the herbal sleep aids

503
00:30:53,360 --> 00:30:56,400
但让我眩晕无力 所以我停用了
leave me groggy, so I-I discontinued,

504
00:30:56,540 --> 00:31:00,300
几乎隔天吃一次唑吡坦
and zolpidem is at most an every-other-day option.

505
00:31:00,440 --> 00:31:03,790
连续两天 每天超过0.5毫克
More than point-five milligrams two days in a row

506
00:31:03,930 --> 00:31:07,030
第二天早上就莫名窝火
produces unmotivated rage the next morning.

507
00:31:08,520 --> 00:31:12,180
如果连续服用三天或以上
And three or more days in a row...

508
00:31:14,760 --> 00:31:16,870
情况会变得更遭
...things get even uglier.

509
00:31:18,460 --> 00:31:20,390
什么
What?

510
00:31:22,740 --> 00:31:28,920
我觉得 你上报得很谨慎
I just... I-I think that’s an extremely careful report.

511
00:31:30,570 --> 00:31:31,990
为什么这么说
How so?

512
00:31:32,130 --> 00:31:34,850
劳拉西泮3毫克或以下
Uh, lorazepam three milligrams or below,

513
00:31:34,990 --> 00:31:39,130
唑吡坦每月20毫克以下
zolpidem below 20 milligrams per month,

514
00:31:39,270 --> 00:31:41,960
还有草药叫南非醉茄是吧
and the herbal, that’s... that’s ashwagandha, right?

515
00:31:42,100 --> 00:31:44,830
-是的 -好的
-Yes. -Yeah. Yeah.

516
00:31:44,970 --> 00:31:46,930
我觉得这些剂量
I think those amounts and dosages

517
00:31:47,070 --> 00:31:49,970
不用上报
are just under my reporting requirements.

518
00:31:50,110 --> 00:31:51,910
你也清楚
And you know that.

519
00:31:52,040 --> 00:31:56,670
你觉得我在蒙你 为了不进入
And you feel it’s duplicitous for me to want to avoid

520
00:31:56,810 --> 00:32:00,640
心理服务上报流程
involvement in psych services reporting chains?

521
00:32:00,780 --> 00:32:02,710
我说过了 我认为你很谨慎
As I said, I-I think it’s careful.

522
00:32:02,850 --> 00:32:05,330
我是这里任务中心的主管 我当然得谨慎了
I’m the head of sig ops; of course I’m careful.

523
00:32:05,470 --> 00:32:07,440
这不是我们在此的目的
Well, that’s not the goal in here.

524
00:32:07,580 --> 00:32:10,920
目的是服从命令
The goal is to satisfy the mandate

525
00:32:11,060 --> 00:32:13,340
这样我才能回去工作
so I can get back to work.

526
00:32:18,310 --> 00:32:23,590
你为什么要跟拉姆罗德·吉米·斯托克斯上床
Why on earth are you sleeping with Ramrod Jimmy Stokes?

527
00:32:24,630 --> 00:32:27,320
-他配不上你 -我们专业点
-He’s beneath you. -Let’s keep this professional.

528
00:32:27,460 --> 00:32:28,490
专业点
Professional?

529
00:32:28,630 --> 00:32:30,290
你跑到我家来
You came to my home.

530
00:32:30,430 --> 00:32:32,390
喝了酒 吃了饭 高谈阔论你的性生活
You drank, you ate, you talked about your sex life.

531
00:32:32,530 --> 00:32:35,020
这算哪门子专业
What in God’s name is professional about that?

532
00:32:35,160 --> 00:32:37,160
也许那个叫观察性访视
Maybe it was an observational visit.

533
00:32:37,300 --> 00:32:38,990
我一直都看在眼里
I’ve had it up to my eyeballs

534
00:32:39,120 --> 00:32:42,060
我被我周围的每一个人监视
being watched by every single person around me.

535
00:32:43,470 --> 00:32:46,510
哦是的 无论如何 把那个记下来
Oh, yes, by all means, write that one down.

536
00:32:46,650 --> 00:32:48,310
偏执多疑
Paranoid ideations.

537
00:32:48,440 --> 00:32:51,690
让上面再给我下6个月的命令
Buy me another mandatory six months.

538
00:32:53,040 --> 00:32:55,800
你知道吗 我总能知道你何时要来
You know, I always know when you’re arriving.

539
00:32:55,930 --> 00:32:59,830
你来之前 我就能感受到你的杀气
Because the aroma of hostility wafts in ahead of you.

540
00:32:59,970 --> 00:33:03,110
你头一回不那么无聊了
Oh, well, that’s the first interesting thing you’ve said.

541
00:33:04,560 --> 00:33:06,570
你和乔治怎么样了
How are things with George?

542
00:33:10,780 --> 00:33:13,160
那天 亚瑟·施蒂格利茨跟我说
The other day, Arthur Stieglitz told me

543
00:33:13,300 --> 00:33:19,580
我对婚姻的投入是我的职业弱点
that my devotion to my marriage is my professional weakness.

544
00:33:19,720 --> 00:33:23,240
我对乔治的爱是我的致命伤
That my feelings for George are a gaping wound

545
00:33:23,380 --> 00:33:26,480
任何人都能利用他来伤害我
through which any idiot can attack me.

546
00:33:27,720 --> 00:33:33,350
他跟我说 我想要的太多 不可能什么都得到
He told me I want too much and that I cannot have it all.

547
00:33:34,350 --> 00:33:36,290
我要顶替他的工作了
I’m going to have his job.

548
00:33:36,420 --> 00:33:38,740
你看着吧
You watch.

549
00:33:38,870 --> 00:33:40,670
他说的对吗
Is he right?

550
00:33:40,810 --> 00:33:42,570
如果这种情况出现
If a situation presents itself,

551
00:33:42,710 --> 00:33:44,330
你会选择婚姻 放弃其他吗
would you choose your marriage over everything else?

552
00:33:44,470 --> 00:33:46,400
我很珍视忠诚
I value loyalty.

553
00:33:46,540 --> 00:33:48,230
对什么的忠诚
To what?

554
00:33:50,850 --> 00:33:53,370
