928
00:58:08,580 --> 00:58:11,210
这里有个陌生人
There is a stranger in our house.

929
00:58:13,550 --> 00:58:16,180
他离开后 我们接到帕夫留克了吗
Have we picked up Pavlichuk since he left?

930
00:58:16,320 --> 00:58:17,700
他没问题
He’s good.

931
00:58:17,830 --> 00:58:20,560
他蜷缩在某辆黑色面包车里
He’s hunched over in a black van somewhere,

932
00:58:20,700 --> 00:58:22,870
准备去干坏事
off to malefact.

933
00:58:23,010 --> 00:58:24,630
呃 好吧 我们的假设是
Uh, well, our assumption is

934
00:58:24,770 --> 00:58:28,090
他的得力助手 前副官安德烈·库里科夫
that his right-hand former lieutenant Andrei Kulikov

935
00:58:28,220 --> 00:58:30,570
现在正在去接他的路上
is en route to pick him up now.

936
00:58:30,710 --> 00:58:32,370
他们的意图尚不清楚
Their intentions are unclear.

937
00:58:32,500 --> 00:58:34,160
今早 库里科夫在苏黎世与一个不知名的人士会面
Kulikov had a meeting with an unknown party in Zurich

938
00:58:34,300 --> 00:58:37,230
我们正在等待相关的影像资料
this morning, so we’re waiting on visuals for that.

939
00:58:37,370 --> 00:58:39,340
嗯嗯 继续
Mm-hmm. Keep at it.

940
00:58:39,480 --> 00:58:41,240
我们应该
Should we...

941
00:58:41,370 --> 00:58:43,200
我们应该通知CIA吗
Should we notify CIA?

942
00:58:43,340 --> 00:58:44,900
哦 去他妈的CIA
Oh, fuck them.

943
00:58:45,030 --> 00:58:47,900
我受够了被当作情报的取款机
I’m sick of being treated like an ATM for intel.

944
00:58:48,040 --> 00:58:50,900
而且我当然也不会让他们看我们出丑
And I’m certainly not showing them our dirty linens.

945
00:58:51,040 --> 00:58:52,420
如果这里有叛徒
If there’s a traitor in the house,

946
00:58:52,560 --> 00:58:54,910
我想在CIA查到之前 查出是谁
I want to know who it is before they do.

947
00:58:55,040 --> 00:58:57,530
这事只能在这里说
This stays in the room.

948
00:59:04,810 --> 00:59:06,750
你说少校 呃
You said the major was, uh...

949
00:59:06,880 --> 00:59:08,370
知道重新定向吗
...aware of the redirect?

950
00:59:08,510 --> 00:59:10,750
是的 我收到了警报并给他打了电话
Yes. I got a signal alert and called him.

951
00:59:10,890 --> 00:59:13,170
-他已经知道了 -嗯
-He already knew. -Hmm.

952
00:59:13,300 --> 00:59:16,690
把他重新分配到巴哈马的某个好地方
Have him reassigned... somewhere lovely, the Bahamas.

953
00:59:16,820 --> 00:59:20,970
告诉他这是升职 立即生效
Tell him it’s a promotion, effective immediately.

954
00:59:21,100 --> 00:59:23,180
他明天就去
He travels tomorrow.

955
00:59:23,310 --> 00:59:25,800
请问 从战略上讲
Can I ask, strategically,

956
00:59:25,940 --> 00:59:28,150
我们为什么在乎帕夫留克跑了
why do we care that Pavlichuk is out?

957
00:59:32,530 --> 00:59:36,290
S-6级别以下 请回避
S-6 and below, please clear.

958
00:59:53,930 --> 00:59:55,590
死危病毒
Severus.

959
00:59:57,660 --> 01:00:00,420
我们相信帕夫留克已经得到了一份实体副本
We believe Pavlichuk has been given a physical copy.

960
01:00:00,560 --> 01:00:02,180
这就是我们监视他的原因
That’s why we watched him.

961
01:00:02,320 --> 01:00:06,220
如果库里科夫设法让他带着病毒回到莫斯科
If Kulikov manages to get him back into Moscow with it,

962
01:00:06,360 --> 01:00:07,630
那就
well...

963
01:00:07,770 --> 01:00:11,260
斯摩尔斯先生 请给我们的同事解释一下
Mr. Smalls, educate our colleagues.

964
01:00:11,400 --> 01:00:13,570
死危病毒是我们与NSA一起开发的
Severus is a Stuxnet polymorph

965
01:00:13,710 --> 01:00:14,950
多晶型蠕虫病毒
we developed with NSA.

966
01:00:15,090 --> 01:00:16,780
它必须通过物理方式
It has to be physically introduced

967
01:00:16,920 --> 01:00:19,680
进入核反应堆以通过气隙
to a nuclear reactor to get past an air gap.

968
01:00:19,820 --> 01:00:24,480
但它一旦进入 就可以瞄准并熔化反应堆堆芯
But once it’s in, it can target and melt down the reactor core.

969
01:00:24,620 --> 01:00:25,820
这是美国网络司令部的行动
It was a CYBERCOM op.

970
01:00:25,960 --> 01:00:28,240
我们为什么要做那个东西
Why the fuck would we make that?

971
01:00:28,380 --> 01:00:30,170
理论上做的出 跟有能力做的出还是有区别的
Theoreticals. Capabilities.

972
01:00:30,310 --> 01:00:31,860
它不应该离开那栋大楼
It shouldn’t have left the building.

973
01:00:32,000 --> 01:00:33,800
我们意识到 如果我们能对他们动手
And we realized, if we can do it to them,

974
01:00:33,940 --> 01:00:36,660
-一旦那玩意儿流到外面 -他们可以对我们动手
-once the thing is out there... -They can do it to us.

975
01:00:36,800 --> 01:00:39,320
是个好主意
It was a good idea.

976
01:00:39,460 --> 01:00:40,700
嗯
Hmm?

977
01:00:40,840 --> 01:00:43,880
灾难将导致政治混乱
A meltdown would cause political havoc.

978
01:00:44,010 --> 01:00:46,710
对于一个卷入无休止战争的敌人
For an enemy involved in an endless war

979
01:00:46,850 --> 01:00:48,400
以及一个摇摇欲坠的政府来说
and a teetering government,

980
01:00:48,540 --> 01:00:51,230
他们会用铁轨把亲爱的领袖赶出莫斯科
they’d run dear leader out of Moscow on a rail.

981
01:00:51,370 --> 01:00:54,020
我们就能一劳永逸地摆脱这个刺头了
We’d be rid of the prick once and for all.

982
01:00:54,160 --> 01:00:56,340
我们没有这样做
We didn’t do it...

983
01:00:58,650 --> 01:01:00,380
但这真他妈是个好主意
...but it was a damn good idea.

984
01:01:00,510 --> 01:01:02,860
看来这里有人也有同样的感觉
It would appear someone here felt the same way.

985
01:01:03,000 --> 01:01:05,590
嗯嗯 重新定向监视视线
Mm-hmm. And redirected the eye

986
01:01:05,730 --> 01:01:09,730
这样帕夫留克就可以带着驱动器逃跑了
so Pavlichuk could escape with the drive.

987
01:01:09,870 --> 01:01:12,630
他现在正在前往俄罗斯的路上 以引发一场灾难
He’s on his way to Russia now to initiate a meltdown,

988
01:01:12,770 --> 01:01:15,670
这他妈将是我们的错
and it’ll be our goddamn fault!

989
01:01:17,770 --> 01:01:19,810
找到泄漏点
Find the leak.

990
01:01:20,910 --> 01:01:22,880
不管用什么方法
Methods won’t be questioned.

991
01:02:08,100 --> 01:02:10,240
这下可不妙
This can’t be good.

992
01:02:10,380 --> 01:02:11,580
的确
It isn’t.

993
01:02:11,720 --> 01:02:13,860
乔治命令重新定向
George ordered the redirect.

994
01:02:14,000 --> 01:02:16,240
我帮助他做到了
I helped him do it.

995
01:02:50,590 --> 01:02:52,320
谢谢
Thanks.

996
01:02:56,250 --> 01:02:57,700
凯瑟琳
Kathryn.

997
01:02:57,840 --> 01:02:59,360
上帝啊 弗雷迪
Jesus, Freddie.

998
01:02:59,490 --> 01:03:01,320
有时间吗
Got a minute?

999
01:03:02,330 --> 01:03:03,810
还有其他人知道吗
Does anyone else know?

1000
01:03:03,950 --> 01:03:05,810
没有
No.

1001
01:03:05,950 --> 01:03:08,160
-你能信任克拉丽莎吗 -不是很信任
-Can you trust Clarissa? -Not particularly.

1002
01:03:08,300 --> 01:03:10,510
-我是说 她不会说出去 -我觉得可以
-To keep it to herself, I mean. -I think so.

1003
01:03:10,640 --> 01:03:12,510
她喜欢乔治 她很担心
She’s fond of George. She’s concerned.

1004
01:03:12,650 --> 01:03:15,340
无论他在进行什么行动 他都处于危险的境地
Whatever operation he’s running, he’s in a very leaky boat.

1005
01:03:15,480 --> 01:03:18,170
如果帕夫留克回到俄罗斯 那就看他自己了
If Pavlichuk gets back to Russia, it’s on him.

1006
01:03:18,310 --> 01:03:19,960
他已经活了35年
He’d get 35 years.

1007
01:03:20,100 --> 01:03:22,480
你能做些什么吗
Is there anything you can do?

1008
01:03:25,620 --> 01:03:27,490
苏黎世怎么样
How was Zurich?

1009
01:03:28,350 --> 01:03:30,840
毫无意义 他一无所有
It was pointless. He had nothing.

1010
01:03:30,970 --> 01:03:32,870
我不知道自己为什么去那里
I don’t know why I was there.

1011
01:03:33,010 --> 01:03:35,840
我花了一整天的时间在FIS追逐冈瑟
I spent the rest of the day chasing down Gunther at FIS,

1012
01:03:35,980 --> 01:03:38,360
但他一无是处
but he was useless.

1013
01:03:38,500 --> 01:03:41,470
你知道为什么乔治会监视你吗
Do you have any idea why George would be watching you?

1014
01:03:41,610 --> 01:03:43,820
毫无头绪
None whatsoever.

1015
01:03:47,850 --> 01:03:49,230
好吧
All right.

1016
01:03:49,370 --> 01:03:51,550
你早上准备好
You be ready in the morning.

1017
01:03:51,680 --> 01:03:53,340
我需要一个晚上来考虑
I need a night to think.

1018
01:03:53,480 --> 01:03:54,760
好
Okay.

1019
01:03:54,900 --> 01:03:57,040
只有你和我
Just you and me.

1020
01:03:57,170 --> 01:03:58,240
是吗
Yes?

1021
01:03:58,380 --> 01:04:00,140
当然
Of course.

1022
01:04:37,390 --> 01:04:39,870
我肯定自己已经被陷害了
I believe I’ve been set up.

1023
01:04:42,390 --> 01:04:44,770
我想我也是
I think I have been, too.

1024
01:04:46,050 --> 01:04:48,910
被弗雷迪 被所有人
By Freddie, of all people.

1025
01:04:49,810 --> 01:04:51,400
为什么
Why?

1026
01:04:53,440 --> 01:04:55,610
嗯 他在耍我
Well, he’s playing me.

1027
01:04:55,750 --> 01:04:58,540
他认为我会采取行动保护你
He thinks I’ll take action to protect you.

1028
01:05:01,030 --> 01:05:02,760
他说得对
And he’s right.

1029
01:05:04,620 --> 01:05:07,040
我会为你杀人 乔治
I will kill for you, George.

1030
01:05:08,970 --> 01:05:10,380
你知道的
You know that.

1031
01:05:15,940 --> 01:05:17,630
弗雷迪偷了死危病毒
Freddie stole Severus.

1032
01:05:17,770 --> 01:05:19,910
啊 也许是 也许不是
Ah, maybe, maybe not.

1033
01:05:20,050 --> 01:05:22,600
这已经不是真的了 不是吗
It’s not really about that anymore, is it?

1034
01:05:22,740 --> 01:05:24,610
不知为什么
Somehow it’s...

1035
01:05:26,750 --> 01:05:28,610
这是关于我们的
...it’s about us.

1036
01:05:30,440 --> 01:05:32,820
有一个计划
There’s a plan.

1037
01:05:32,960 --> 01:05:35,200
还有一个对策
And a counterplan.

1038
01:05:35,340 --> 01:05:39,760
一个利用你接近我，另一个利用我来接近你
One is using you to get to me, the other, me to get to you.

1039
01:05:43,140 --> 01:05:45,970
那么，我们打算怎么应对
Well, what are we going to do about that?

1040
01:05:47,250 --> 01:05:49,010
扰乱他们
Disrupt.

1041
01:05:49,150 --> 01:05:50,800
他们的所有计划
All of it.

1042
01:05:52,460 --> 01:05:55,330
逼他主动就范
Bait someone into an overreaction.

1043
01:05:58,020 --> 01:06:00,610
会不会又出现一些新麻烦需要收拾
Will there be another mess to clean up?

1044
01:06:02,540 --> 01:06:04,850
做对了才会有
Only if we do it right.

1045
01:06:52,730 --> 01:06:55,730
你要是早点打电话就好了 我连钓具都没有
Wish you’d called sooner. I didn’t really have any gear.

1046
01:06:55,870 --> 01:06:57,800
先上船吧
Hop in.

1047
01:06:59,460 --> 01:07:01,220
钓鱼我不在行
Fishing’s not really my thing.

1048
01:07:01,360 --> 01:07:03,570
你只需要有些耐心
Patience. All you need.

1049
01:07:09,400 --> 01:07:11,880
我们不需要花太久
We’ll be back in plenty of time.

1050
01:07:13,230 --> 01:07:15,440
这里更适合思考
It’s easier to think out here.

1051
01:07:30,080 --> 01:07:32,220
我需要一些帮助
I need something.

1052
01:07:33,940 --> 01:07:36,670
需要追踪安德烈·库里科夫 最后位置在苏黎世
Geofencing on Andrei Kulikov. Last known is Zurich.

1053
01:07:36,810 --> 01:07:38,600
我要对他的手机进行动态追踪
I want a moving trace on his cell,

1054
01:07:38,740 --> 01:07:41,430
不能留下记录
and I want it to be un-logged.

1055
01:07:41,570 --> 01:07:44,230
我可不想为了你们两个疯子住监狱
I’m not going to prison for you psychos.

1056
01:07:44,370 --> 01:07:46,510
哦 你现在才说这个是不是有点晚了
Oh, you’re too far in to worry about that now,

1057
01:07:46,640 --> 01:07:48,160
你不觉得吗
don’t you think?

1058
01:07:55,070 --> 01:07:56,520
真他妈的天生一对
Fucking made for each other.

1059
01:07:58,280 --> 01:08:00,550
我想安排几场测谎
I’d like to set up a series of polygraphs.

1060
01:08:00,690 --> 01:08:01,930
今天
Today.

1061
01:08:02,070 --> 01:08:04,250
在沃克斯豪尔的房间
The usual room at Vauxhall.

1062
01:08:05,150 --> 01:08:06,970
你打算测谁
Who did you have in mind?

1063
01:08:07,110 --> 01:08:08,840
弗雷迪·斯莫尔斯
Freddie Smalls.

1064
01:08:08,980 --> 01:08:10,670
克拉丽莎·杜博斯
Clarissa Dubose.

1065
01:08:10,810 --> 01:08:13,500
佐伊·沃恩博士
Dr. Zoe Vaughan.

1066
01:08:13,640 --> 01:08:15,360
怎么还有她
Why her?

1067
01:08:15,500 --> 01:08:18,120
弗雷迪过去八个月每周见她两次
Freddie saw her twice a week for the past eight months.

1068
01:08:18,260 --> 01:08:19,920
有重大嫌疑
Leakage.

1069
01:08:21,020 --> 01:08:22,510
我也见过她
And I’ve seen her, too.

1070
01:08:22,640 --> 01:08:25,300
我知道 那把你自己也加上吧
I know. Put yourself down as well.

1071
01:08:26,370 --> 01:08:28,380
公正公开
Transparency.

1072
01:08:31,720 --> 01:08:33,140
还有其他人吗
Anyone else?

1073
01:08:33,280 --> 01:08:35,280
暂时没有
Not for the moment.

1074
01:08:37,760 --> 01:08:41,010
那么 关于瑞士银行的问题
So, that Swiss banking issue.

1075
01:08:41,150 --> 01:08:43,390
我一直想跟你跟进一下
I’d been meaning to follow up with you.

1076
01:08:43,530 --> 01:08:44,870
当然人们会想到
Of course one’s mind

1077
01:08:45,010 --> 01:08:47,840
这可能和死危病毒有关
goes to a possible Severus connection.

1078
01:08:47,980 --> 01:08:49,360
我也想到过
That had occurred to me.

1079
01:08:49,500 --> 01:08:51,330
是么
Had it?

1080
01:08:52,330 --> 01:08:54,710
看起来确实有关联
It would appear to be linked.

1081
01:08:55,820 --> 01:08:58,680
你跟别人分享过你的怀疑吗
Have you shared your suspicions with anyone else?

1082
01:09:02,790 --> 01:09:04,450
当然没有
Of course not.

1083
01:09:06,170 --> 01:09:08,170
但你依然肯定
But you still feel certain of the identity

1084
01:09:08,310 --> 01:09:11,280
开通离岸账户的人是谁吗
of the person who opened the offshore account?

1085
01:09:11,420 --> 01:09:13,140
我不确定
No.

1086
01:09:13,280 --> 01:09:15,040
不确定 问题就在这里
No, that’s the thing.

1087
01:09:15,180 --> 01:09:17,670
这就是为什么我一直想跟你跟进
That’s why I’d been meaning to follow up with you.

1088
01:09:17,800 --> 01:09:19,360
哦
Oh.

1089
01:09:21,010 --> 01:09:22,390
「玛格丽特·兰福德」
"Margaret Langford."

1090
01:09:22,530 --> 01:09:24,470
凯瑟琳在08年使用的护照名字
The passport name that Kathryn used in ’08.

1091
01:09:24,600 --> 01:09:26,090
结果发现系统出了点问题
Turns out there was some sort of glitch.

1092
01:09:26,230 --> 01:09:28,060
它被系统反复回收
It was repeatedly recycled by the system,

1093
01:09:28,190 --> 01:09:29,540
在SIS内部流传了十年
passed around SIS for a decade.

1094
01:09:29,680 --> 01:09:31,130
至少被使用了十几次
There’s at least a dozen uses.

1095
01:09:31,270 --> 01:09:33,370
四五十条边境记录
40 or 50 border records.

1096
01:09:34,370 --> 01:09:36,030
你居然漏掉了这个 有点奇怪
Seems odd you’d miss that.

1097
01:09:36,170 --> 01:09:37,270
是的
Yes.

1098
01:09:37,410 --> 01:09:40,070
是啊 我恨死自己了
Yeah, I’m kicking myself.

1099
01:09:40,210 --> 01:09:41,240
这太马虎了
It was sloppy.

1100
01:09:41,380 --> 01:09:43,620
重点是
The point is...

1101
01:09:43,760 --> 01:09:45,180
可能是任何人
it could’ve been anyone.

1102
01:09:47,280 --> 01:09:49,180
我们不再盯着凯瑟琳了
We’re no longer looking at Kathryn.

1103
01:09:49,320 --> 01:09:51,320
「我们」吗
"We"?

1104
01:09:54,320 --> 01:09:56,220
你和我
You and me.

1105
01:09:58,400 --> 01:10:00,850
喔喔我该做什么
Whoa, whoa! Wh-What do I do?

1106
01:10:02,370 --> 01:10:04,780
坐壁上观
Let him run for a minute.

1107
01:10:10,340 --> 01:10:12,060
给艾玛的美式咖啡
Americano for Emma.

1108
01:10:12,200 --> 01:10:13,860
谢谢
Thank you.

1109
01:10:37,020 --> 01:10:39,470
适时信号区域锁定 这是追踪登录
Live cell zone lock. That’s the trace log-in.

1110
01:10:39,610 --> 01:10:41,090
